 from theatrical distributors, while also pissing off numerous studio partn=
ers. Imax C.E.O. Rich Gelfond has threatened a
=E2=80=9Cnuclear option=E2=80=9D to ensure cooperation=E2=80=94but what lev=
ers are actually at his disposal?

