e Trump-Putin pact upon the third anniversary of Russia=E2=80=99s invasion.=
 Lauren Sherman inspects the brain drain at Rihanna=E2=80=99s once billion-=
dollar intimates brand, Savage x Fenty. Matt Belloni
scoops the departure of legendary movie producer Kathleen Kennedy at Lucasf=
ilm. And John Ourand gets the ticktock on the MLB-ESPN divorce.

